"{\"uid\": \"chronofhorse.com-article-21-and-twice-retired-forever-young-wundermaske-makes-olympic-history-in-paris\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"Tuesday, Dec. 2, 2025 Paris-July 27 The aptly named Forever Young Wundermaske, a 21-year-old Oldenburg gelding (Weltbekannt-Deer Rose, Deerhound) ridden by Ronald Zabala Goetschel of Ecuador, made history today as the oldest horse ever to start at the Olympic Games.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 268, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 54, \"end\": 67, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Forever_Young_(Alphaville_song)\", \"score\": 0.6523250760534972, \"rank\": 0.34106891701835723, \"text\": \"Forever Young\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q2188189\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Forever_Young_(Alphaville_song)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Forever_Young_(Alphaville_song)\"}, {\"begin\": 95, \"end\": 104, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oldenburger\", \"score\": 0.9999999997430677, \"rank\": 2.55986272268006e-10, \"text\": \"Oldenburg\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oldenburger\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oldenburger\"}, {\"begin\": 185, \"end\": 192, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ecuador\", \"score\": 0.9966597186791684, \"rank\": 0.0016677106197962401, \"text\": \"Ecuador\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ecuador\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ecuador\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Dec.\", \"from\": 9, \"to\": 13}, {\"ngram\": \"Paris-July\", \"from\": 22, \"to\": 32}, {\"ngram\": \"(Weltbekannt-Deer Rose\", \"from\": 111, \"to\": 133}, {\"ngram\": \"Ronald Zabala Goetschel\", \"from\": 156, \"to\": 179}, {\"ngram\": \"history\", \"from\": 197, \"to\": 204}, {\"ngram\": \"the oldest horse\", \"from\": 214, \"to\": 230}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Games\", \"from\": 248, \"to\": 265}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The pair scored 37.70 and stand 51st after dressage.\", \"from\": 269, \"to\": 321, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The pair\", \"from\": 269, \"to\": 277}, {\"ngram\": \"dressage\", \"from\": 312, \"to\": 320}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have Googled that, I have done ChatGPT and everything,\\\" said Zabala Goetschel, who at 57, is also the oldest eventing rider at this year's Games.\", \"from\": 323, \"to\": 471, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"ChatGPT\", \"from\": 357, \"to\": 364}, {\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 369, \"to\": 379}, {\"ngram\": \"Zabala Goetschel\", \"from\": 387, \"to\": 403}, {\"ngram\": \"the oldest eventing rider\", \"from\": 424, \"to\": 449}, {\"ngram\": \"this year's Games\", \"from\": 453, \"to\": 470}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The oldest in eventing has been 19.\", \"from\": 472, \"to\": 508, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"eventing\", \"from\": 487, \"to\": 495}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And this guy is 21, and he's flying; he never gets tired, never get ssick and never had an injury in his life.\", \"from\": 509, \"to\": 619, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this guy\", \"from\": 513, \"to\": 521}, {\"ngram\": \"an injury\", \"from\": 597, \"to\": 606}, {\"ngram\": \"his life\", \"from\": 610, \"to\": 618}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And I have thought that he has been retired twice.\\\"\", \"from\": 620, \"to\": 671, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The gelding has been known simply as Wundermaske for most of his long career, but Zabala Goetschel officially changed his name with the F\\u00e9d\\u00e9ration Equestre International to Forever Young Wundermaske on July 4, according to FEI records-just days before the deadline for Olympic entries.\", \"from\": 673, \"to\": 958, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 896, \"end\": 899, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Federation_for_Equestrian_Sports\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.044395013975821e-45, \"text\": \"FEI\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Federation_for_Equestrian_Sports\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Federation_for_Equestrian_Sports\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The gelding\", \"from\": 673, \"to\": 684}, {\"ngram\": \"Wundermaske\", \"from\": 710, \"to\": 721}, {\"ngram\": \"his long career\", \"from\": 734, \"to\": 749}, {\"ngram\": \"Zabala Goetschel\", \"from\": 755, \"to\": 771}, {\"ngram\": \"his name\", \"from\": 791, \"to\": 799}, {\"ngram\": \"the F\\u00e9d\\u00e9ration Equestre International\", \"from\": 805, \"to\": 842}, {\"ngram\": \"Forever Young Wundermaske\", \"from\": 846, \"to\": 871}, {\"ngram\": \"July\", \"from\": 875, \"to\": 879}, {\"ngram\": \"the deadline\", \"from\": 925, \"to\": 937}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic entries\", \"from\": 942, \"to\": 957}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Around the barn, though, the bald-faced gelding is called \\\"Patchito.\\\"\", \"from\": 959, \"to\": 1028, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the barn\", \"from\": 966, \"to\": 974}, {\"ngram\": \"the bald-faced gelding\", \"from\": 984, \"to\": 1006}, {\"ngram\": \"\\\"Patchito\", \"from\": 1017, \"to\": 1026}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Patchito was originally campaigned by Sharon White, who completed the Kentucky and Pau (France) CCI4* events (now CCI5*-L) with him in 2014, placing 23rd and 19th, respectively.\", \"from\": 1030, \"to\": 1207, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1068, \"end\": 1080, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Whites\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.869339616754901e-17, \"text\": \"Sharon White\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q215380\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Whites\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Whites\"}, {\"begin\": 1100, \"end\": 1108, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kentucky\", \"score\": 0.9999369555204383, \"rank\": 6.117730274403881e-05, \"text\": \"Kentucky\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kentucky\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kentucky\"}, {\"begin\": 1113, \"end\": 1116, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pau_Grand_Prix\", \"score\": 0.9693898910877234, \"rank\": 0.02741921874583268, \"text\": \"Pau\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pau_Grand_Prix\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pau_Grand_Prix\"}, {\"begin\": 1118, \"end\": 1124, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9997428886395271, \"rank\": 0.00024205870369507624, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Patchito\", \"from\": 1030, \"to\": 1038}, {\"ngram\": \"events\", \"from\": 1132, \"to\": 1138}, {\"ngram\": \"-L\", \"from\": 1149, \"to\": 1151}, {\"ngram\": \"23rd\", \"from\": 1179, \"to\": 1183}, {\"ngram\": \"19th\", \"from\": 1188, \"to\": 1192}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She sold him to Zabala Goetschel in 2015, who competed at the 2018 FEI World Equestrian Games in Tryon, North Carolina, finishing 64th.\", \"from\": 1208, \"to\": 1343, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1270, \"end\": 1301, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2018_FEI_World_Equestrian_Games\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"2018 FEI World Equestrian Games\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2018_FEI_World_Equestrian_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2018_FEI_World_Equestrian_Games\"}, {\"begin\": 1305, \"end\": 1326, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tryon,_North_Carolina\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Tryon, North Carolina\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tryon,_North_Carolina\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tryon,_North_Carolina\"}, {\"begin\": 1305, \"end\": 1326, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tryon,_North_Carolina\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Tryon, North Carolina\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tryon,_North_Carolina\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tryon,_North_Carolina\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Zabala Goetschel\", \"from\": 1224, \"to\": 1240}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I retired him at 19, [then] I brought him back to qualify when they postponed the Olympics.\", \"from\": 1345, \"to\": 1437, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1424, \"to\": 1436}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I said, I owe this to him because it was not his fault that I could not get points [to qualify] because I was injured twice in 2019; I fell off of another horse,\\\" Zabala Goetschel said.\", \"from\": 1438, \"to\": 1623, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his fault\", \"from\": 1483, \"to\": 1492}, {\"ngram\": \"points\", \"from\": 1514, \"to\": 1520}, {\"ngram\": \"another horse\", \"from\": 1585, \"to\": 1598}, {\"ngram\": \"Zabala Goetschel\", \"from\": 1601, \"to\": 1617}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"So I brought him back, we went to Tryon in November 2020, and he qualified for Olympics.\", \"from\": 1624, \"to\": 1713, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1659, \"end\": 1664, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Uptown_Charlotte\", \"score\": 0.9999999999990905, \"rank\": 7.842438031356761e-13, \"text\": \"Tryon\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Uptown_Charlotte\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Uptown_Charlotte\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"November\", \"from\": 1668, \"to\": 1676}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympics\", \"from\": 1704, \"to\": 1712}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And then I did not have enough points.\", \"from\": 1714, \"to\": 1752, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"enough points\", \"from\": 1738, \"to\": 1751}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I retired him again, and I bought horses again,\\\" Zabala Goetschel said.\", \"from\": 1754, \"to\": 1826, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"horses\", \"from\": 1789, \"to\": 1795}, {\"ngram\": \"Zabala Goetschel\", \"from\": 1804, \"to\": 1820}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But his new mounts got injured.\", \"from\": 1827, \"to\": 1858, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his new mounts\", \"from\": 1831, \"to\": 1845}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"So Patchito has come back!\", \"from\": 1859, \"to\": 1886, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Patchito\", \"from\": 1863, \"to\": 1871}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He takes all the bullets, and he loves it.\", \"from\": 1887, \"to\": 1929, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"all the bullets\", \"from\": 1896, \"to\": 1911}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When I retired him the first time, I had to send him into another barn in my farm because he was crazy.\", \"from\": 1930, \"to\": 2033, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"another barn\", \"from\": 1988, \"to\": 2000}, {\"ngram\": \"my farm\", \"from\": 2004, \"to\": 2011}]}, {\"sentence\": \"[It's like he] told me, 'I want to go, come on, I am here.'\", \"from\": 2034, \"to\": 2093, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"[So I moved him] because he was desperate.\", \"from\": 2094, \"to\": 2136, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But then the groom told me that he's running like crazy in the paddock all day, like, 'I want to do something,' and so here we are.\", \"from\": 2137, \"to\": 2268, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the groom\", \"from\": 2146, \"to\": 2155}, {\"ngram\": \"the paddock\", \"from\": 2196, \"to\": 2207}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 2237, \"to\": 2246}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He has the same problem I have: We think we are younger than what we are.\\\"\", \"from\": 2269, \"to\": 2343, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the same problem\", \"from\": 2276, \"to\": 2292}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Given Patchito's age, Zabala Goetschel has a careful regimen for fitness.\", \"from\": 2345, \"to\": 2418, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Patchito's age\", \"from\": 2351, \"to\": 2365}, {\"ngram\": \"Zabala Goetschel\", \"from\": 2367, \"to\": 2383}, {\"ngram\": \"a careful regimen\", \"from\": 2388, \"to\": 2405}, {\"ngram\": \"fitness\", \"from\": 2410, \"to\": 2417}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have a different system to train him,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 2419, \"to\": 2469, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a different system\", \"from\": 2427, \"to\": 2445}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Since they arrived in Europe in February, \\\"I have been riding him six days a week, but back home he only gets ridden once a week, once every 10 days.\", \"from\": 2471, \"to\": 2620, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Europe\", \"from\": 2493, \"to\": 2499}, {\"ngram\": \"February\", \"from\": 2503, \"to\": 2511}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I do a lot of walker.\", \"from\": 2621, \"to\": 2642, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 2626, \"to\": 2631}, {\"ngram\": \"walker\", \"from\": 2635, \"to\": 2641}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I have a trotter with rubber shavings, so they trot without weight.\", \"from\": 2643, \"to\": 2710, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a trotter\", \"from\": 2650, \"to\": 2659}, {\"ngram\": \"rubber shavings\", \"from\": 2665, \"to\": 2680}, {\"ngram\": \"weight\", \"from\": 2703, \"to\": 2709}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And I gallop him; I jump him once a month.\", \"from\": 2711, \"to\": 2753, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He knows what to do.\\\"\", \"from\": 2754, \"to\": 2775, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Zabala Goetschel has been working on his own fitness as well, losing 11 pounds since arriving in Europe.\", \"from\": 2777, \"to\": 2881, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Zabala Goetschel\", \"from\": 2777, \"to\": 2793}, {\"ngram\": \"his own fitness\", \"from\": 2814, \"to\": 2829}, {\"ngram\": \"11 pounds\", \"from\": 2846, \"to\": 2855}, {\"ngram\": \"Europe\", \"from\": 2874, \"to\": 2880}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"A pound means a lot.\", \"from\": 2883, \"to\": 2904, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A pound\", \"from\": 2884, \"to\": 2891}, {\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 2898, \"to\": 2903}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am trying to just be thankful with him and be grateful and try to weigh less and stay fit,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 2905, \"to\": 3007, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He wants to make cross-country as easy as possible for his partner, and he said he's looking forward to Saturday.\", \"from\": 3009, \"to\": 3122, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"country\", \"from\": 3032, \"to\": 3039}, {\"ngram\": \"his partner\", \"from\": 3064, \"to\": 3075}, {\"ngram\": \"Saturday\", \"from\": 3113, \"to\": 3121}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's a beautiful course,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 3124, \"to\": 3159, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a beautiful course\", \"from\": 3130, \"to\": 3148}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think the straighter routes are easier than the options, even though they could be bigger, but I think that they are easier.\", \"from\": 3160, \"to\": 3287, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the straighter routes\", \"from\": 3169, \"to\": 3190}, {\"ngram\": \"the options\", \"from\": 3207, \"to\": 3218}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So I do not think I will take any options; I do not think so.\", \"from\": 3288, \"to\": 3349, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"any options\", \"from\": 3318, \"to\": 3329}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However he feels, we will see.\\\"\", \"from\": 3350, \"to\": 3381, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Their FEI results this spring include several withdrawals and a cross-country elimination for an error on course, but at their last international competition before the Olympics, the Avenches CCIO4*-NC-S (Switzerland) in June, they finished 21st with a clean, conservative cross-country round.\", \"from\": 3383, \"to\": 3676, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3389, \"end\": 3392, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Federation_for_Equestrian_Sports\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.044395013975821e-45, \"text\": \"FEI\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Federation_for_Equestrian_Sports\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Federation_for_Equestrian_Sports\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"several withdrawals\", \"from\": 3421, \"to\": 3440}, {\"ngram\": \"a cross-country elimination\", \"from\": 3445, \"to\": 3472}, {\"ngram\": \"an error\", \"from\": 3477, \"to\": 3485}, {\"ngram\": \"course\", \"from\": 3489, \"to\": 3495}, {\"ngram\": \"their last international competition\", \"from\": 3504, \"to\": 3540}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 3548, \"to\": 3560}, {\"ngram\": \"-NC\", \"from\": 3581, \"to\": 3584}, {\"ngram\": \"-S\", \"from\": 3584, \"to\": 3586}, {\"ngram\": \"June\", \"from\": 3604, \"to\": 3608}, {\"ngram\": \"21st\", \"from\": 3624, \"to\": 3628}, {\"ngram\": \"a clean, conservative cross-country round\", \"from\": 3634, \"to\": 3675}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Zabala Goetschel also competed at the London Olympics in 2012, finishing 43rd on Master Boy.\", \"from\": 3678, \"to\": 3770, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3716, \"end\": 3731, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.922713956098939e-16, \"text\": \"London Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Zabala Goetschel\", \"from\": 3678, \"to\": 3694}, {\"ngram\": \"Master Boy\", \"from\": 3759, \"to\": 3769}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Chronicle has a reporter on site at the Paris Olympics.See all of our coverage here.\", \"from\": 3772, \"to\": 3860, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The Chronicle\", \"from\": 3772, \"to\": 3785}, {\"ngram\": \"a reporter\", \"from\": 3790, \"to\": 3800}, {\"ngram\": \"site\", \"from\": 3804, \"to\": 3808}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Olympics\", \"from\": 3812, \"to\": 3830}, {\"ngram\": \"our coverage\", \"from\": 3842, \"to\": 3854}]}, {\"sentence\": \"See our eventing coverage.\", \"from\": 3862, \"to\": 3888, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"our eventing coverage\", \"from\": 3866, \"to\": 3887}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Full results.\", \"from\": 3890, \"to\": 3903, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Full results\", \"from\": 3890, \"to\": 3902}]}, {\"sentence\": \"By submitting your email, you agree to our Terms of Service and Privacy Policy.\", \"from\": 3905, \"to\": 3984, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"your email\", \"from\": 3919, \"to\": 3929}, {\"ngram\": \"our Terms\", \"from\": 3944, \"to\": 3953}, {\"ngram\": \"Service\", \"from\": 3957, \"to\": 3964}, {\"ngram\": \"Privacy Policy\", \"from\": 3969, \"to\": 3983}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You may also receive promotional emails from The Chronicle of the Horse.\", \"from\": 3985, \"to\": 4057, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"promotional emails\", \"from\": 4006, \"to\": 4024}, {\"ngram\": \"The Chronicle\", \"from\": 4030, \"to\": 4043}, {\"ngram\": \"the Horse\", \"from\": 4047, \"to\": 4056}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You can opt out at any time.\", \"from\": 4058, \"to\": 4086, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"any time\", \"from\": 4077, \"to\": 4085}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For Customers Company Terms of Use Copyright \\u00a9 2025 The Chronicle of the Horse Copyright \\u00a9 2025 The Chronicle of the Horse\", \"from\": 4088, \"to\": 4214, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Customers Company Terms\", \"from\": 4092, \"to\": 4115}, {\"ng